item.description:
our very own "4-on-the-floor", one of my fave rock'n roll bands, is getting down at the Princeston Station in Chelmsford (no, they haven't thrown us out yet, well not all of us...sorry D :) about 9-9:30. come to dance or get there about 8pm for dinner (insist on separate check, or eat at bar). you'll see me about 8:30, will do intros then, but after the music starts, I'm on the dance floor...YOU look for ME there :)
someone wants to coordinate dinner, please put in your reply, or post.
suz
item.how_to_find_us: look for the loud bunch, with the meetup sign hiding on the table somewhere....
